<td>Identifies your practice to Google</td>
<td>Homepage, about page</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>MedicalClinic</code></td>
<td>Specifies clinic type</td>
<td>Homepage</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>Service</code></td>
